 -- What can teachers do to combat their students' apathy?

在这些条目还发现' apathy '：
在英文解释里：
couldn't-give-a-damn attitude - indifference - lack of enthusiasm - lack of feeling - lack of interest - laziness - lethargy - phlegm
中文：
漠然

